msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Agnosis Gallery Overview"
msgstr "Agnosis Gallery Akopọ"

#: blocks/gallery-overview/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Proportional, randomised artwork grid across all artists. Shows featured "
"artworks first, respects per-artist budget, supports medium filtering and "
"pagination."
msgstr ""
"Akojọpọ iṣẹ ọnà ti o ni ibamu, ti a ṣe ni airotẹlẹ lori gbogbo awọn oṣere. "
"Ṣafihan awọn iṣẹ ọnà ti a fi han akọkọ, bọwọ fun isuna oṣere kọọkan, ṣe "
"atilẹyin àlẹmọ ọna kika ati iyipada oju-iwe."

