"Lists the logged-in artist's pending artwork submissions for review and "
"approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Akojọ awọn iṣẹ ọnà ti o wa fun atunyẹwo ati ifọwọsi nipasẹ oṣere ti o wọle. "
"Fi eyi si oju-iwe /my-submissions/ rẹ tabi ninu awoṣe Olutọpa Aaye kan."

